l\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104agi1665702784377.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/agi1665702784377.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/agi1665702784377.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"agi1665702784377\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">$WEBGEN_X_FOR_DEFAULT\n  </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines the default value of the x-for placeholder attribute for associated labels\n    in static server pages.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"agi1665702784377__p_d144131e1_d144132e1_d144133e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$WEBGEN_X_FOR_DEFAULT</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code> |\n        <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code></p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"agi1665702784377__section_emj_1jn_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d872756e65\">Values</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"agi1665702784377__ul_r4m_bjn_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"agi1665702784377__li_d50327e1_d50328e1_d50329e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>—<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webgen</span>\n          generates a <code class=\"ph codeph\">for</code> attribute for each associated label. It has the same\n          value as the field's <code class=\"ph codeph\">name</code> attribute. <p class=\"p\" id=\"agi1665702784377__p_d144137e1_d144138e1_d144139e1\">This is equivalent to adding\n              <code class=\"ph codeph\">x-for=\"1\"</code> to each <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;xsubst type=\"label\"&gt;</code> tag in\n            USP layouts.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"agi1665702784377__li_d50330e1_d50331e1_d50332e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>—<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webgen</span> does not\n          generate an <code class=\"ph codeph\">id</code> attribute with the same value as the <code class=\"ph codeph\">name</code>\n          attribute. <p class=\"p\" id=\"agi1665702784377__p_d144140e1_d144141e1_d144142e1\">This is equivalent to adding\n              <code class=\"ph codeph\">x-for=\"0\"</code> to each <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;xsubst type=\"label\"&gt;</code> tag\n            for fields in the USP layout.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"agi1665702784377__section_cz2_djn_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d872756e120\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"agi1665702784377__table_d17465e1_d17466e1_d17467e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Any application assignment file </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[WEB]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"agi1665702784377__section_rgn_fjn_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d872756e168\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"agi1665702784377__p_d144149e1_d144150e1_d144151e1\">By default, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webgen</span> does not\n        generate <code class=\"ph codeph\">for</code> attributes for associated labels in static server pages. It is\n        possible to change this behavior globally by setting\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$WEBGEN_X_FOR_DEFAULT</span> to <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>, or locally by adding\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">x-for=\"1\"</code> to the <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-subst type=\"label\"&gt;</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">For more information, see the \"x-for\" topic.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"agi1665702784377__section_vp2_3jn_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d872756e199\">Example: Generating <code class=\"ph codeph\">for</code> Attributes by Default </h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"agi1665702784377__pre_qy5_kjn_lwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[WEB]\n$WEBGEN_X_ID_DEFAULT = True ; cause webgen to generate 'id' attributes for fields\n$WEBGEN_X_ID_INSNAME = True ; cause webgen to append the USP instance name to the id attribute\n$WEBGEN_X_FOR_DEFAULT = True ; cause webgen to generate 'for' attribute for associated labels</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fdp1719467376341.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>&lt;x-subst type=\"WidgetType\"&gt;</a><p>XHTML placeholder for the USP widget and field data that will be generated in the HTML sent to the browser.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525671\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525671\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$WEBGEN_X_FOR_DEFAULT Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $WEBGEN_X_FOR_DEFAULT Determines the default value of the x-for placeholder attribute for associated labels in static server pages. $WEBGEN_X_FOR_DEFAULT { = } 1 | 0 Values 1 — webgen generates a for attribute for each associated label. It has the same value as the field's name attribute. This is equivalent to adding x-for=\"1\" to each <xsubst type=\"label\"> tag in USP layouts. 0 — webgen does not generate an id attribute with the same value as the name attribute. This is equivalent to adding x-for=\"0\" to each <xsubst type=\"label\"> tag for fields in the USP layout. Defaults Assignment file: Any application assignment file Section: [WEB] Default value: 0 Description By default, webgen does not generate for attributes for associated labels in static server pages. It is possible to change this behavior globally by setting $WEBGEN_X_FOR_DEFAULT to 1 , or locally by adding x-for=\"1\" to the <x-subst type=\"label\"> . For more information, see the \"x-for\" topic. Example: Generating for Attributes by Default [WEB] $WEBGEN_X_ID_DEFAULT = True ; cause webgen to generate 'id' attributes for fields $WEBGEN_X_ID_INSNAME = True ; cause webgen to append the USP instance name to the id attribute $WEBGEN_X_FOR_DEFAULT = True ; cause webgen to generate 'for' attribute for associated labels Copy Related Links <x-subst type=\"WidgetType\"> XHTML placeholder for the USP widget and field data that will be generated in the HTML sent to the browser. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}